						<div class="postbody">I don't know if he reads this forum, but if the guy who designed the PowerPak is lurking about, I have a question:
<br />
<br />Would you be willing to custom-make a PowerPak for the Famicom in a Famicom cartridge body? Or sell the parts to do so with a diagram?
<br />
<br />I'd rather have a dedicated "PowerPak FC" than use a bulky adapter setup...
<br />
<br />It's something to consider offfering regularly too, for the Famicom crowd. 
<br />
<br />-Xious</div>

